1ï¸. Why This Project Was Created (Project Aim)
Problem
DAO EV TECH manages multiple electric vehicles.
 Each EV generates critical health data like:
Speed
Battery voltage & current
Motor RPM
Temperature
SOC (State of Charge)
Without a system:
Faults go unnoticed
Vehicles fail unexpectedly
Maintenance costs increase
Project Aim
This project builds a mini real-world EV IoT monitoring system that:
Simulates real EV sensor data
Stores data locally (for reliability)
Sends data to the cloud using MQTT
Detects faults locally (edge processing)
Displays live data on a dashboard
This is the foundation of remote diagnostics & predictive maintenance for EV fleets.
